18 /*
19  * Scripts for spells with SPELLFAMILY_GENERIC which cannot be included in AI script file
20  * of creature using it or can't be bound to any player class.
21  * Ordered alphabetically using scriptname.
22  * Scriptnames of files in this file should be prefixed with "spell_gen_"
23  */

49 // 46642 - 5,000 Gold
50 class spell_gen_5000_gold : public SpellScript
51 {
52  PrepareSpellScript(spell_gen_5000_gold);
53 
54  void HandleScript(SpellEffIndex /*effIndex*/)
55  {
56  if (Player* target = GetHitPlayer())
57  {
58  target->ModifyMoney(5000 * GOLD);
59  }
60  }
61 
62  void Register() override
63  {
64  OnEffectHitTarget += SpellEffectFn(spell_gen_5000_gold::HandleScript, EFFECT_0, SPELL_EFFECT_SCRIPT_EFFECT);
65  }
66 };

68 // 24401 - Test Pet Passive
69 class spell_gen_model_visible : public AuraScript
70 {
71 public:
72  PrepareAuraScript(spell_gen_model_visible)
73 
74  bool Load() override
75  {
76  _modelId = 0;
77  _hasFlag = false;
78  return true;
79  }
80 
81  void HandleEffectApply(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
82  {
83  _modelId = GetUnitOwner()->GetDisplayId();
84  _hasFlag = GetUnitOwner()->HasFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_NOT_SELECTABLE);
85  for (uint8 i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
86  _itemId.at(i) = GetUnitOwner()->GetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID + i);
87 
88  GetUnitOwner()->SetDisplayId(11686);
89  GetUnitOwner()->SetFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_NOT_SELECTABLE);
90  for (uint8 i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
91  GetUnitOwner()->SetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID + i, 0);
92  }
93 
94  void HandleEffectRemove(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
95  {
96  GetUnitOwner()->SetDisplayId(_modelId);
97  if (!_hasFlag)
98  GetUnitOwner()->RemoveFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_NOT_SELECTABLE);
99  for (uint8 i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
100  GetUnitOwner()->SetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID + i, _itemId.at(i));
101  }
102 
103  void Register() override
104  {
105  OnEffectApply += AuraEffectApplyFn(spell_gen_model_visible::HandleEffectApply, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_DUMMY, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL);
106  OnEffectRemove += AuraEffectRemoveFn(spell_gen_model_visible::HandleEffectRemove, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_DUMMY, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL);
107  }
108 
109 private:
110  std::array<uint32, 3> _itemId = { {0, 0, 0} };
111  uint32 _modelId;
112  bool _hasFlag;
113 };

115 // 51640 - Taunt Flag Targeting
116 class spell_the_flag_of_ownership : public SpellScript
117 {
118  PrepareSpellScript(spell_the_flag_of_ownership);
119 
120  bool haveTarget;
121  bool Load() override
122  {
123  haveTarget = false;
124  return true;
125  }
126 
127  void HandleScript(SpellEffIndex /*effIndex*/)
128  {
129  Unit* caster = GetCaster();
130  if (!caster || caster->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
131  return;
132  Player* target = GetHitPlayer();
133  if (!target)
134  return;
135  caster->CastSpell(target, 52605, true);
136  char buff[100];
137  sprintf(buff, "%s plants the Flag of Ownership in the corpse of %s.", caster->GetName().c_str(), target->GetName().c_str());
138  caster->TextEmote(buff, caster);
139  haveTarget = true;
140  }
141 
142  void FilterTargets(std::list<WorldObject*>& targets)
143  {
144  for( std::list<WorldObject*>::iterator itr = targets.begin(); itr != targets.end(); )
145  {
146  if ((*itr)->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER || (*itr)->ToPlayer()->IsAlive())
147  {
148  targets.erase(itr);
149  itr = targets.begin();
150  continue;
151  }
152  ++itr;
153  }
154  }
155 
156  void HandleFinish()
157  {
158  Unit* caster = GetCaster();
159  if (!caster || !caster->ToPlayer())
160  return;
161 
162  if (!haveTarget)
163  {
164  caster->ToPlayer()->RemoveSpellCooldown(GetSpellInfo()->Id, true);
165  Spell::SendCastResult(caster->ToPlayer(), GetSpellInfo(), 0, SPELL_FAILED_BAD_TARGETS);
166  }
167  }
168 
169  void Register() override
170  {
171  AfterCast += SpellCastFn(spell_the_flag_of_ownership::HandleFinish);
172  OnEffectHitTarget += SpellEffectFn(spell_the_flag_of_ownership::HandleScript, EFFECT_0, SPELL_EFFECT_DUMMY);
173  OnObjectAreaTargetSelect += SpellObjectAreaTargetSelectFn(spell_the_flag_of_ownership::FilterTargets, EFFECT_0, TARGET_CORPSE_SRC_AREA_ENEMY);
174  }
175 };

177 /* 51060 - Have Withered Batwing
178  51068 - Have Muddy Mire Maggot
179  51088 - Have Amberseed
180  51094 - Have Chilled Serpent Mucus */
181 class spell_gen_have_item_auras : public AuraScript
182 {
183  PrepareAuraScript(spell_gen_have_item_auras)
184 
185  void HandleEffectApply(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
186  {
187  Unit* target = GetTarget();
188  if (target && target->ToPlayer())
189  {
190  uint32 entry = 0;
191  switch (GetSpellInfo()->Id)
192  {
193  case 51060: // Have Withered Batwing
194  entry = 28294;
195  break;
196  case 51068: // Have Muddy Mire Maggot
197  entry = 28293;
198  break;
199  case 51094: // Have Chilled Serpent Mucus
200  entry = 28296;
201  break;
202  case 51088: // Have Amberseed
203  entry = 28295;
204  break;
205  }
206 
207  if (entry)
208  target->ToPlayer()->KilledMonsterCredit(entry);
209  }
210  }
211 
212  void Register() override
213  {
214  OnEffectApply += AuraEffectApplyFn(spell_gen_have_item_auras::HandleEffectApply, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_DUMMY, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL);
215  }
216 };

218 /* 54355 - Detonation
219  57099 - Landmine Knockback Achievement Aura */
220 class spell_gen_mine_sweeper : public SpellScript
221 {
222  PrepareSpellScript(spell_gen_mine_sweeper);
223 
224  void HandleSchoolDMG(SpellEffIndex /*effIndex*/)
225  {
226  Unit* caster = GetCaster();
227  Player* target = GetHitPlayer();
228  if (!target)
229  return;
230 
231  target->RemoveAurasByType(SPELL_AURA_MOUNTED);
232  caster->CastSpell(target, 54402, true);
233  }
234 
235  void HandleScriptEffect(SpellEffIndex /*effIndex*/)
236  {
237  if (Unit* target = GetHitPlayer())
238  if (Aura* aur = target->GetAura(GetSpellInfo()->Id))
239  if (aur->GetStackAmount() >= 10)
240  target->CastSpell(target, 57064, true);
241  }
242 
243  void Register() override
244  {
245  if (m_scriptSpellId == 54355)
246  OnEffectHitTarget += SpellEffectFn(spell_gen_mine_sweeper::HandleSchoolDMG, EFFECT_0, SPELL_EFFECT_SCHOOL_DAMAGE);
247  else
248  OnEffectHitTarget += SpellEffectFn(spell_gen_mine_sweeper::HandleScriptEffect, EFFECT_0, SPELL_EFFECT_SCRIPT_EFFECT);
249  }
250 };

252 /* 20004 - Life Steal
253  20005 - Chilled
254  20007 - Holy Strength */
255 class spell_gen_reduced_above_60 : public SpellScript
256 {
257  PrepareSpellScript(spell_gen_reduced_above_60);
258 
259  void RecalculateDamage()
260  {
261  if (Unit* target = GetHitUnit())
262  if (target->getLevel() > 60)
263  {
264  int32 damage = GetHitDamage();
265  AddPct(damage, -4 * int8(std::min(target->getLevel(), uint8(85)) - 60)); // prevents reduce by more than 100%
266  SetHitDamage(damage);
267  }
268  }
269 
270  void Register() override
271  {
272  OnHit += SpellHitFn(spell_gen_reduced_above_60::RecalculateDamage);
273  }
274 };
275 
276 class spell_gen_reduced_above_60_aura : public AuraScript
277 {
278  PrepareAuraScript(spell_gen_reduced_above_60_aura);
279 
280  void CalculateAmount(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, int32& amount, bool& /*canBeRecalculated*/)
281  {
282  if (Unit* owner = GetUnitOwner())
283  if (owner->getLevel() > 60)
284  AddPct(amount, -4 * int8(std::min(owner->getLevel(), uint8(85)) - 60)); // prevents reduce by more than 100%
285  }
286 
287  void Register() override
288  {
289  if (m_scriptSpellId != 20004) // Lifestealing enchange - no aura effect
290  DoEffectCalcAmount += AuraEffectCalcAmountFn(spell_gen_reduced_above_60_aura::CalculateAmount, EFFECT_ALL, SPELL_AURA_ANY);
291  }
292 };

296 class spell_gen_relocaste_dest : public SpellScript
297 {

299 public:
300  spell_gen_relocaste_dest(float x, float y, float z, float o) : _x(x), _y(y), _z(z), _o(o) { }
301 
302  void RelocateDest()
303  {
304  Position const offset = {_x, _y, _z, _o};
305  const_cast<WorldLocation*>(GetExplTargetDest())->RelocateOffset(offset);
306  }
307 
308  void Register() override

311  }
312 
313 private:

317 /* 55640 - Lightweave Embroidery
318  67698 - Item - Coliseum 25 Normal Healer Trinket
319  67752 - Item - Coliseum 25 Heroic Healer Trinket
320  69762 - Unchained Magic */
321 class spell_gen_allow_proc_from_spells_with_cost : public AuraScript
322 {
323  PrepareAuraScript(spell_gen_allow_proc_from_spells_with_cost);
324 
325  bool CheckProc(ProcEventInfo& eventInfo)
326  {
327  SpellInfo const* spellInfo = eventInfo.GetSpellInfo();
328  if (!spellInfo)
329  return false;
330 
331  // xinef: Spells with no damage class and physical school only are not treated as spells
332  if ((eventInfo.GetTypeMask() & (PROC_FLAG_DONE_SPELL_NONE_DMG_CLASS_NEG | PROC_FLAG_DONE_SPELL_NONE_DMG_CLASS_POS)) && spellInfo->SchoolMask == SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL)
333  return false;
334 
335  // xinef: holy nova exception
336  if (spellInfo->SpellFamilyName == SPELLFAMILY_PRIEST && spellInfo->SpellIconID == 1874)
337  return spellInfo->HasEffect(SPELL_EFFECT_HEAL);
338 
339  // xinef: Holy Shock exception...
340  return spellInfo->ManaCost > 0 || spellInfo->ManaCostPercentage > 0 || (spellInfo->SpellFamilyName == SPELLFAMILY_PALADIN && spellInfo->SpellIconID == 156);
341  }
342 
343  void Register() override
344  {
345  DoCheckProc += AuraCheckProcFn(spell_gen_allow_proc_from_spells_with_cost::CheckProc);
346  }
347 };

349 /* 32727 - Arena Preparation
350  44521 - Preparation */
351 class spell_gen_bg_preparation : public AuraScript
352 {
353  PrepareAuraScript(spell_gen_bg_preparation)
354 
355  void HandleEffectApply(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
356  {
357  GetTarget()->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_DAMAGE, SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_ALL, true);
358  }
359 
360  void HandleEffectRemove(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
361  {
362  GetTarget()->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_DAMAGE, SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_ALL, false);
363  }
364 
365  void CalcPeriodic(AuraEffect const* /*effect*/, bool& isPeriodic, int32& amplitude)
366  {
367  isPeriodic = true;
368  amplitude = 3 * IN_MILLISECONDS;
369  }
370 
371  void Update(AuraEffect* /*effect*/)
372  {
373  if (Player* player = GetUnitOwner()->GetCharmerOrOwnerPlayerOrPlayerItself())
374  if (MapEntry const* mapEntry = sMapStore.LookupEntry(player->GetMapId()))
375  if ((GetId() == 32727 && mapEntry->IsBattleArena()) || (GetId() == 44521 && mapEntry->IsBattleground()))
376  if (Battleground* bg = player->GetBattleground())
377  if (bg->GetStatus() == STATUS_WAIT_JOIN)
378  return;
379  SetMaxDuration(1);
380  SetDuration(1);
381  }
382 
383  void Register() override
384  {
385  OnEffectApply += AuraEffectApplyFn(spell_gen_bg_preparation::HandleEffectApply, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_MOD_POWER_COST_SCHOOL_PCT, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL);
386  OnEffectRemove += AuraEffectRemoveFn(spell_gen_bg_preparation::HandleEffectRemove, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_MOD_POWER_COST_SCHOOL_PCT, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL);
387 
388  DoEffectCalcPeriodic += AuraEffectCalcPeriodicFn(spell_gen_bg_preparation::CalcPeriodic, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_MOD_POWER_COST_SCHOOL_PCT);
389  OnEffectUpdatePeriodic += AuraEffectUpdatePeriodicFn(spell_gen_bg_preparation::Update, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_MOD_POWER_COST_SCHOOL_PCT);
390  }
391 };

421 /* 61013 - Warlock Pet Scaling 05
422  61017 - Hunter Pet Scaling 04 */
423 class spell_pet_hit_expertise_scalling : public AuraScript
424 {
425  PrepareAuraScript(spell_pet_hit_expertise_scalling)
426 
427  int32 CalculatePercent(float hitChance, float cap, float maxChance)
428  {
429  return (hitChance / cap) * maxChance;
430  }
431 
432  void CalculateHitAmount(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, int32& amount, bool& /*canBeRecalculated*/)
433  {
434  if (Player* modOwner = GetUnitOwner()->GetSpellModOwner())
435  {
436  if (modOwner->getClass() == CLASS_HUNTER)
437  amount = CalculatePercent(modOwner->m_modRangedHitChance, 8.0f, 8.0f);
438  else if (modOwner->getPowerType() == POWER_MANA)
439  amount = CalculatePercent(modOwner->m_modSpellHitChance, 17.0f, 8.0f);
440  else
441  amount = CalculatePercent(modOwner->m_modMeleeHitChance, 8.0f, 8.0f);
442  }
443  }
444 
445  void CalculateSpellHitAmount(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, int32& amount, bool& /*canBeRecalculated*/)
446  {
447  if (Player* modOwner = GetUnitOwner()->GetSpellModOwner())
448  {
449  if (modOwner->getClass() == CLASS_HUNTER)
450  amount = CalculatePercent(modOwner->m_modRangedHitChance, 8.0f, 17.0f);
451  else if (modOwner->getPowerType() == POWER_MANA)
452  amount = CalculatePercent(modOwner->m_modSpellHitChance, 17.0f, 17.0f);
453  else
454  amount = CalculatePercent(modOwner->m_modMeleeHitChance, 8.0f, 17.0f);
455  }
456  }
457 
458  void CalculateExpertiseAmount(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, int32& amount, bool& /*canBeRecalculated*/)
459  {
460  if (Player* modOwner = GetUnitOwner()->GetSpellModOwner())
461  {
462  if (modOwner->getClass() == CLASS_HUNTER)
463  amount = CalculatePercent(modOwner->m_modRangedHitChance, 8.0f, 26.0f);
464  else if (modOwner->getPowerType() == POWER_MANA)
465  amount = CalculatePercent(modOwner->m_modSpellHitChance, 17.0f, 26.0f);
466  else
467  amount = CalculatePercent(modOwner->m_modMeleeHitChance, 8.0f, 26.0f);
468  }
469  }
470 
471  void HandleEffectApply(AuraEffect const* aurEff, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
472  {
473  GetUnitOwner()->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_STATE, aurEff->GetAuraType(), true, SPELL_BLOCK_TYPE_POSITIVE);
474  }
475 
476  void CalcPeriodic(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, bool& isPeriodic, int32& amplitude)
477  {
478  if (!GetUnitOwner()->IsPet())
479  return;
480 
481  isPeriodic = true;
482  amplitude = 3 * IN_MILLISECONDS;
483  }
484 
485  void HandlePeriodic(AuraEffect const* aurEff)
486  {
487  PreventDefaultAction();
488  GetEffect(aurEff->GetEffIndex())->RecalculateAmount();
489  }
490 
491  void Register() override
492  {
493  DoEffectCalcAmount += AuraEffectCalcAmountFn(spell_pet_hit_expertise_scalling::CalculateHitAmount, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_MOD_HIT_CHANCE);
494  DoEffectCalcAmount += AuraEffectCalcAmountFn(spell_pet_hit_expertise_scalling::CalculateSpellHitAmount, EFFECT_1, SPELL_AURA_MOD_SPELL_HIT_CHANCE);
495  DoEffectCalcAmount += AuraEffectCalcAmountFn(spell_pet_hit_expertise_scalling::CalculateExpertiseAmount, EFFECT_2, SPELL_AURA_MOD_EXPERTISE);
496 
497  OnEffectApply += AuraEffectApplyFn(spell_pet_hit_expertise_scalling::HandleEffectApply, EFFECT_ALL, SPELL_AURA_ANY, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL);
498  DoEffectCalcPeriodic += AuraEffectCalcPeriodicFn(spell_pet_hit_expertise_scalling::CalcPeriodic, EFFECT_ALL, SPELL_AURA_ANY);
499  OnEffectPeriodic += AuraEffectPeriodicFn(spell_pet_hit_expertise_scalling::HandlePeriodic, EFFECT_ALL, SPELL_AURA_ANY);
500  }
501 };

588 // 59630 - Black Magic
589 class spell_gen_black_magic_enchant : public AuraScript
590 {

596  if (!spellInfo)
597  return false;
598 
599  // Xinef: Old 'code'
600  if (eventInfo.GetTypeMask() & PROC_FLAG_DONE_SPELL_MAGIC_DMG_CLASS_NEG)
601  return true;
602 
603  // Implement Black Magic enchant Bug
604  if (spellInfo->SpellFamilyName == SPELLFAMILY_DRUID)
605  if (spellInfo->SpellIconID == 2857 /*SPELL_INFECTED_WOUNDS*/ || spellInfo->SpellIconID == 147 /*SPELL_SHRED*/ || spellInfo->SpellFamilyFlags[1] & 0x400 /*SPELL_MANGLE_(CAT)*/)
606  return true;
607 
608  return false;
609  }

1345  {

1347  }
1348 
1349  SpellCastResult CheckIfCorpseNear()
1350  {
1351  Unit* caster = GetCaster();
1352  float max_range = GetSpellInfo()->GetMaxRange(false);
1353  WorldObject* result = nullptr;
1354  // search for nearby enemy corpse in range
1355  Acore::AnyDeadUnitSpellTargetInRangeCheck check(caster, max_range, GetSpellInfo(), TARGET_CHECK_CORPSE);
1356  Acore::WorldObjectSearcher<Acore::AnyDeadUnitSpellTargetInRangeCheck> searcher(caster, result, check);
1357  Cell::VisitWorldObjects(caster, searcher, max_range);
1358  if (!result)
1359  {
1360  Cell::VisitGridObjects(caster, searcher, max_range);
1361  }
1362  if (!result)
1363  {
1364  return SPELL_FAILED_NO_EDIBLE_CORPSES;
1365  }
1366  return SPELL_CAST_OK;
1367  }
1368 
1369  void HandleDummy(SpellEffIndex /*effIndex*/)
1370  {
1371  GetCaster()->CastSpell(GetCaster(), SPELL_CANNIBALIZE_TRIGGERED, false);
1372  }
1373 
1374  void Register() override
1375  {
1376  OnEffectHit += SpellEffectFn(spell_gen_cannibalize::HandleDummy, EFFECT_0, SPELL_EFFECT_DUMMY);
1377  OnCheckCast += SpellCheckCastFn(spell_gen_cannibalize::CheckIfCorpseNear);
1378  }

1483  if (!sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(SPELL_NETHERBLOOM_POLLEN_1 + i))

1485  return true;

1489  {
1490  PreventHitDefaultEffect(effIndex);
1491 
1492  if (Unit* target = GetHitUnit())
1493  {
1494  // 25% chance of casting a random buff
1495  if (roll_chance_i(75))
1496  return;
1497 
1498  // triggered spells are 28703 to 28707
1499  // Note: some sources say, that there was the possibility of
1500  // receiving a debuff. However, this seems to be removed by a patch.
1501 
1502  // don't overwrite an existing aura
1503  for (uint8 i = 0; i < 5; ++i)
1504  if (target->HasAura(SPELL_NETHERBLOOM_POLLEN_1 + i))
1505  return;
1506 
1507  target->CastSpell(target, SPELL_NETHERBLOOM_POLLEN_1 + urand(0, 4), true);
1508  }
1509  }
1510

1512  {

1767 /* 29266, 57685, 58951, 70592, 70628, 74490 - Permanent Feign Death

1770 class spell_gen_creature_permanent_feign_death : public AuraScript
1771 {
1772  PrepareAuraScript(spell_gen_creature_permanent_feign_death);
1773 
1774  void HandleEffectApply(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
1775  {
1776  Unit* target = GetTarget();
1777  target->SetFlag(UNIT_DYNAMIC_FLAGS, UNIT_DYNFLAG_DEAD);
1778  target->SetFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS_2, UNIT_FLAG2_FEIGN_DEATH);
1779  target->SetFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_IMMUNE_TO_PC | UNIT_FLAG_IMMUNE_TO_NPC);
1780 
1781  if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_UNIT)
1782  target->ToCreature()->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
1783  }
1784 
1785  void HandleEffectRemove(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
1786  {
1787  Unit* target = GetTarget();
1788  target->RemoveFlag(UNIT_DYNAMIC_FLAGS, UNIT_DYNFLAG_DEAD);
1789  target->RemoveFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS_2, UNIT_FLAG2_FEIGN_DEATH);
1790  target->RemoveFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_IMMUNE_TO_PC | UNIT_FLAG_IMMUNE_TO_NPC);
1791 
1792  if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_UNIT)
1793  target->ToCreature()->SetReactState(REACT_AGGRESSIVE);
1794  }
1795 
1796  void Register() override
1797  {
1798  OnEffectApply += AuraEffectApplyFn(spell_gen_creature_permanent_feign_death::HandleEffectApply, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_DUMMY, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL);
1799  OnEffectRemove += AuraEffectApplyFn(spell_gen_creature_permanent_feign_death::HandleEffectRemove, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_DUMMY, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL);

1829  void HandleScript()
1830  {
1831  Player* player = GetCaster()->ToPlayer();

1833  // Spell::SendSpellCooldown() skips all spells with TRIGGERED_IGNORE_SPELL_AND_CATEGORY_CD
1834  player->AddSpellAndCategoryCooldowns(GetSpellInfo(), GetCastItem() ? GetCastItem()->GetEntry() : 0, GetSpell());
1835 
1836  if (player->GetTeamId(true) == TEAM_HORDE)
1837  {
1838  if (GetSpellInfo()->Id == SPELL_WILL_OF_THE_FORSAKEN_COOLDOWN_TRIGGER)

1842  player->GetSession()->SendPacket(&data);
1843  }
1844  else
1845  {
1846  WorldPacket data(SMSG_INITIAL_SPELLS, (1 + 2 + 2 + 4 + 2 + 2 + 4 + 4));
1847  data << uint8(0);
1848  data << uint16(0);
1849  data << uint16(1);
1850  data << uint32(42292); // PvP Trinket spell
1851  data << uint16(0); // cast item id
1852  data << uint16(GetSpellInfo()->GetCategory()); // spell category
1853  data << uint32(0);
1854  data << uint32(GetSpellInfo()->CategoryRecoveryTime);
1855  player->GetSession()->SendPacket(&data);
1856 
1857  WorldPacket data2;
1858  player->BuildCooldownPacket(data2, SPELL_COOLDOWN_FLAG_INCLUDE_GCD, SPELL_PVP_TRINKET, GetSpellInfo()->CategoryRecoveryTime); // PvP Trinket spell
1859  player->GetSession()->SendPacket(&data2);
1860  }
1861  }
1862  }

2076  void OnApply(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
2077  {
2078  Unit* caster = GetCaster();
2079  Unit* target = GetTarget();
2080  if (!caster)
2081  return;
2082 
2083  switch (GetSpellInfo()->Id)
2084  {
2085  case SPELL_COPY_WEAPON_AURA:
2086  case SPELL_COPY_WEAPON_2_AURA:
2087  case SPELL_COPY_WEAPON_3_AURA:
2088  {
2089  prevItem = target->GetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID);
2090 
2091  if (Player* player = caster->ToPlayer())
2092  {
2093  if (Item* mainItem = player->GetItemByPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, EQUIPMENT_SLOT_MAINHAND))
2094  target->SetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID, mainItem->GetEntry());
2095  }
2096  else
2097  target->SetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID, caster->GetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID));
2098  break;
2099  }
2100  case SPELL_COPY_OFFHAND_AURA:
2101  case SPELL_COPY_OFFHAND_2_AURA:
2102  {
2103  prevItem = target->GetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID) + 1;
2104 
2105  if (Player* player = caster->ToPlayer())
2106  {
2107  if (Item* offItem = player->GetItemByPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, EQUIPMENT_SLOT_OFFHAND))
2108  target->SetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID + 1, offItem->GetEntry());
2109  }
2110  else
2111  target->SetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID + 1, caster->GetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID + 1));
2112  break;
2113  }
2114  case SPELL_COPY_RANGED_AURA:
2115  {
2116  prevItem = target->GetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID) + 2;
2117 
2118  if (Player* player = caster->ToPlayer())
2119  {
2120  if (Item* rangedItem = player->GetItemByPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, EQUIPMENT_SLOT_RANGED))
2121  target->SetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID + 2, rangedItem->GetEntry());
2122  }
2123  else
2124  target->SetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID + 2, caster->GetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID + 2));
2125  break;
2126  }
2127  default:
2128  break;
2129  }
2130  }

2132  void OnRemove(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)

2141  target->SetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID, prevItem);
2142  break;
2143  case SPELL_COPY_OFFHAND_AURA:
2144  case SPELL_COPY_OFFHAND_2_AURA:
2145  target->SetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID + 1, prevItem);
2146  break;
2147  case SPELL_COPY_RANGED_AURA:
2148  target->SetUInt32Value(UNIT_VIRTUAL_ITEM_SLOT_ID + 2, prevItem);
2149  break;
2150  default:
2151  break;
2152  }
2153  }

2221  {
2222  _applyTimes.push_back(World::GetGameTimeMS());
2223  stackAmount++;
2224  }
2225 
2226  // pop stack if it expired for us
2227  if (_applyTimes.front() + GetMaxDuration() < World::GetGameTimeMS())
2228  {
2229  stackAmount--;
2230  ModStackAmount(-1, AURA_REMOVE_BY_EXPIRE);
2231  }
2232 
2233  // dont cast this spell on every tick
2234  if (stackAmount >= 15 && stackAmount < 40)
2235  {
2236  stackAmount = 40;
2237  GetTarget()->CastSpell(GetTarget(), SPELL_TURKEY_VENGEANCE, true, nullptr, aurEff, GetCasterGUID());
2238  }
2239  }

2365 class spell_gen_vehicle_scaling_aura: public AuraScript
2366 {
2367  PrepareAuraScript(spell_gen_vehicle_scaling_aura);
2368 
2369  bool Load() override
2370  {
2371  return GetCaster() && GetCaster()->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER && GetOwner()->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_UNIT;
2372  }
2373 
2374  void CalculateAmount(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, int32& amount, bool& /*canBeRecalculated*/)
2375  {
2376  Unit* caster = GetCaster();
2377  float factor;
2378  uint16 baseItemLevel;
2379 
2381  switch (GetId())
2382  {
2383  case SPELL_GEAR_SCALING:
2384  factor = 1.0f;
2385  baseItemLevel = 205;
2386  break;
2387  default:
2388  factor = 1.0f;
2389  baseItemLevel = 170;
2390  break;
2391  }
2392 
2393  float avgILvl = caster->ToPlayer()->GetAverageItemLevel();
2394  if (avgILvl < baseItemLevel)
2395  return;
2396 
2397  amount = uint16((avgILvl - baseItemLevel) * factor);
2398  }
2399 
2400  void Register() override
2401  {

2686 /* DOCUMENTATION: Break-Shield spells
2687  Break-Shield spells can be classified in three groups:
2688 
2689  - Spells on vehicle bar used by players:
2690  + EFFECT_0: SCRIPT_EFFECT
2691  + EFFECT_1: NONE
2692  + EFFECT_2: NONE
2693  - Spells cast by players triggered by script:
2694  + EFFECT_0: SCHOOL_DAMAGE
2695  + EFFECT_1: SCRIPT_EFFECT
2696  + EFFECT_2: FORCE_CAST
2697  - Spells cast by NPCs on players:
2698  + EFFECT_0: SCHOOL_DAMAGE
2699  + EFFECT_1: SCRIPT_EFFECT
2700  + EFFECT_2: NONE
2701 
2702  In the following script we handle the SCRIPT_EFFECT for effIndex EFFECT_0 and EFFECT_1.
2703  - When handling EFFECT_0 we're in the "Spells on vehicle bar used by players" case
2704  and we'll trigger "Spells cast by players triggered by script"
2705  - When handling EFFECT_1 we're in the "Spells cast by players triggered by script"
2706  or "Spells cast by NPCs on players" so we'll search for the first defend layer and drop it.
2707 */
2708 
2709 enum BreakShieldSpells
2710 {
2711  SPELL_BREAK_SHIELD_DAMAGE_2K = 62626,
2712  SPELL_BREAK_SHIELD_DAMAGE_10K = 64590,
2713 
2714  SPELL_BREAK_SHIELD_TRIGGER_FACTION_MOUNTS = 62575, // Also on ToC5 mounts
2715  SPELL_BREAK_SHIELD_TRIGGER_CAMPAING_WARHORSE = 64595,
2716  SPELL_BREAK_SHIELD_TRIGGER_UNK = 66480,
2717  SPELL_BREAK_SHIELD_TRIGGER_SUNDERING_THURST = 63825
2718 };
2719 
2720 /* 62575, 62626, 64342, 64590, 64595, 64686, 65147, 66480, 68504 - Shield-Breaker
2721  63233 - Necrocution
2722  63825 - Sundering Thrust
2723  64507 - Shield-Breaker Counter */
2724 class spell_gen_break_shield : public SpellScript
2725 {
2726  PrepareSpellScript(spell_gen_break_shield)
2727 
2728  void HandleScriptEffect(SpellEffIndex effIndex)
2729  {
2730  Unit* target = GetHitUnit();
2731 
2732  switch (effIndex)
2733  {
2734  case EFFECT_0: // On spells wich trigger the damaging spell (and also the visual)
2735  {
2736  uint32 spellId;
2737 
2738  switch (GetSpellInfo()->Id)
2739  {
2740  case SPELL_BREAK_SHIELD_TRIGGER_UNK:
2741  case SPELL_BREAK_SHIELD_TRIGGER_CAMPAING_WARHORSE:
2742  spellId = SPELL_BREAK_SHIELD_DAMAGE_10K;
2743  break;
2744  case SPELL_BREAK_SHIELD_TRIGGER_FACTION_MOUNTS:
2745  case SPELL_BREAK_SHIELD_TRIGGER_SUNDERING_THURST:
2746  spellId = SPELL_BREAK_SHIELD_DAMAGE_2K;
2747  break;
2748  default:
2749  return;
2750  }
2751 
2752  if (Unit* rider = GetCaster()->GetCharmer())
2753  rider->CastSpell(target, spellId, false);
2754  else
2755  GetCaster()->CastSpell(target, spellId, false);
2756  break;
2757  }
2758  case EFFECT_1: // On damaging spells, for removing a defend layer
2759  {
2760  Unit::AuraApplicationMap const& auras = target->GetAppliedAuras();
2761  for (Unit::AuraApplicationMap::const_iterator itr = auras.begin(); itr != auras.end(); ++itr)
2762  {
2763  if (Aura* aura = itr->second->GetBase())
2764  {
2765  SpellInfo const* auraInfo = aura->GetSpellInfo();
2766  if (auraInfo && auraInfo->SpellIconID == 2007 && aura->HasEffectType(SPELL_AURA_MOD_DAMAGE_PERCENT_TAKEN))
2767  {
2768  aura->ModStackAmount(-1, AURA_REMOVE_BY_ENEMY_SPELL);
2769  // Remove dummys from rider (Necessary for updating visual shields)
2770  if (Unit* rider = target->GetCharmer())
2771  if (Aura* defend = rider->GetAura(aura->GetId()))
2772  defend->ModStackAmount(-1, AURA_REMOVE_BY_ENEMY_SPELL);
2773  break;
2774  }
2775  }
2776  }
2777  break;
2778  }
2779  default:
2780  break;
2781  }
2782  }
2783 
2784  void Register() override
2785  {
2786  OnEffectHitTarget += SpellEffectFn(spell_gen_break_shield::HandleScriptEffect, EFFECT_FIRST_FOUND, SPELL_EFFECT_SCRIPT_EFFECT);
2787  }
2788 };
2789 
2790 /* DOCUMENTATION: Charge spells
2791  Charge spells can be classified in four groups:
2792 
2793  - Spells on vehicle bar used by players:
2794  + EFFECT_0: SCRIPT_EFFECT
2795  + EFFECT_1: TRIGGER_SPELL
2796  + EFFECT_2: NONE
2797  - Spells cast by player's mounts triggered by script:
2798  + EFFECT_0: CHARGE
2799  + EFFECT_1: TRIGGER_SPELL
2800  + EFFECT_2: APPLY_AURA
2801  - Spells cast by players on the target triggered by script:
2802  + EFFECT_0: SCHOOL_DAMAGE
2803  + EFFECT_1: SCRIPT_EFFECT
2804  + EFFECT_2: NONE
2805  - Spells cast by NPCs on players:
2806  + EFFECT_0: SCHOOL_DAMAGE
2807  + EFFECT_1: CHARGE
2808  + EFFECT_2: SCRIPT_EFFECT
2809 
2810  In the following script we handle the SCRIPT_EFFECT and CHARGE
2811  - When handling SCRIPT_EFFECT:
2812  + EFFECT_0: Corresponds to "Spells on vehicle bar used by players" and we make player's mount cast
2813  the charge effect on the current target , "Spells cast by player's mounts triggered by script").
2814  + EFFECT_1 and EFFECT_2: Triggered when "Spells cast by player's mounts triggered by script" hits target,
2815  corresponding to "Spells cast by players on the target triggered by script" and "Spells cast by
2816  NPCs on players" and we check Defend layers and drop a charge of the first found.
2817  - When handling CHARGE:
2818  + Only launched for "Spells cast by player's mounts triggered by script", makes the player cast the
2819  damaging spell on target with a small chance of failing it.
2820 */
2821 
2822 enum ChargeSpells
2823 {
2824  SPELL_CHARGE_DAMAGE_8K5 = 62874,
2825  SPELL_CHARGE_DAMAGE_20K = 68498,
2826  SPELL_CHARGE_DAMAGE_45K = 64591,
2827 
2828  SPELL_CHARGE_CHARGING_EFFECT_8K5 = 63661,
2829  SPELL_CHARGE_CHARGING_EFFECT_20K_1 = 68284,
2830  SPELL_CHARGE_CHARGING_EFFECT_20K_2 = 68501,
2831  SPELL_CHARGE_CHARGING_EFFECT_45K_1 = 62563,
2832  SPELL_CHARGE_CHARGING_EFFECT_45K_2 = 66481,
2833 
2834  SPELL_CHARGE_TRIGGER_FACTION_MOUNTS = 62960,
2835  SPELL_CHARGE_TRIGGER_TRIAL_CHAMPION = 68282,
2836 
2837  SPELL_CHARGE_MISS_EFFECT = 62977,
2838 };

2840 // 62563, 62874, 62960, 63003, 63010, 63661, 64591, 66481, 68282, 68284, 68321, 68498, 68501 - Charge
2841 class spell_gen_mounted_charge : public SpellScript
2842 {
2843  PrepareSpellScript(spell_gen_mounted_charge)
2844 
2845  void HandleScriptEffect(SpellEffIndex effIndex)
2846  {
2847  Unit* target = GetHitUnit();
2848 
2849  switch (effIndex)
2850  {
2851  case EFFECT_0: // On spells wich trigger the damaging spell (and also the visual)
2852  {
2853  uint32 spellId;
2854 
2855  switch (GetSpellInfo()->Id)
2856  {
2857  case SPELL_CHARGE_TRIGGER_TRIAL_CHAMPION:
2858  spellId = SPELL_CHARGE_CHARGING_EFFECT_20K_1;
2859  break;
2860  case SPELL_CHARGE_TRIGGER_FACTION_MOUNTS:
2861  spellId = SPELL_CHARGE_CHARGING_EFFECT_8K5;
2862  break;
2863  default:
2864  return;
2865  }
2866 
2867  // If target isn't a training dummy there's a chance of failing the charge
2868  if (!target->HasFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_DISABLE_MOVE) && roll_chance_f(12.5f))
2869  spellId = SPELL_CHARGE_MISS_EFFECT;
2870 
2871  if (Unit* vehicle = GetCaster()->GetVehicleBase())
2872  vehicle->CastSpell(target, spellId, false);
2873  else
2874  GetCaster()->CastSpell(target, spellId, false);
2875  break;
2876  }
2877  case EFFECT_1: // On damaging spells, for removing a defend layer
2878  case EFFECT_2:
2879  {
2880  Unit::AuraApplicationMap const& auras = target->GetAppliedAuras();
2881  for (Unit::AuraApplicationMap::const_iterator itr = auras.begin(); itr != auras.end(); ++itr)
2882  {
2883  if (Aura* aura = itr->second->GetBase())
2884  {
2885  SpellInfo const* auraInfo = aura->GetSpellInfo();
2886  if (auraInfo && auraInfo->SpellIconID == 2007 && aura->HasEffectType(SPELL_AURA_MOD_DAMAGE_PERCENT_TAKEN))
2887  {
2888  aura->ModStackAmount(-1, AURA_REMOVE_BY_ENEMY_SPELL);
2889  // Remove dummys from rider (Necessary for updating visual shields)
2890  if (Unit* rider = target->GetCharmer())
2891  if (Aura* defend = rider->GetAura(aura->GetId()))
2892  defend->ModStackAmount(-1, AURA_REMOVE_BY_ENEMY_SPELL);
2893  break;
2894  }
2895  }
2896  }
2897  break;
2898  }
2899  }
2900  }
2901 
2902  void HandleChargeEffect(SpellEffIndex /*effIndex*/)
2903  {
2904  uint32 spellId;
2905 
2906  switch (GetSpellInfo()->Id)
2907  {
2908  case SPELL_CHARGE_CHARGING_EFFECT_8K5:
2909  spellId = SPELL_CHARGE_DAMAGE_8K5;
2910  break;
2911  case SPELL_CHARGE_CHARGING_EFFECT_20K_1:
2912  case SPELL_CHARGE_CHARGING_EFFECT_20K_2:
2913  spellId = SPELL_CHARGE_DAMAGE_20K;
2914  break;
2915  case SPELL_CHARGE_CHARGING_EFFECT_45K_1:
2916  case SPELL_CHARGE_CHARGING_EFFECT_45K_2:
2917  spellId = SPELL_CHARGE_DAMAGE_45K;
2918  break;
2919  default:
2920  return;
2921  }
2922 
2923  if (Unit* rider = GetCaster()->GetCharmer())
2924  rider->CastSpell(GetHitUnit(), spellId, false);
2925  else
2926  GetCaster()->CastSpell(GetHitUnit(), spellId, false);
2927  }
2928 
2929  void Register() override
2930  {
2931  SpellInfo const* spell = sSpellMgr->AssertSpellInfo(m_scriptSpellId);
2932 
2933  if (spell->HasEffect(SPELL_EFFECT_SCRIPT_EFFECT))
2934  OnEffectHitTarget += SpellEffectFn(spell_gen_mounted_charge::HandleScriptEffect, EFFECT_FIRST_FOUND, SPELL_EFFECT_SCRIPT_EFFECT);
2935 
2936  if (spell->Effects[EFFECT_0].Effect == SPELL_EFFECT_CHARGE)
2937  OnEffectHitTarget += SpellEffectFn(spell_gen_mounted_charge::HandleChargeEffect, EFFECT_0, SPELL_EFFECT_CHARGE);
2938  }
2939 };

2941 enum DefendVisuals

2948 // 62552, 62719, 66482 - Defend
2949 class spell_gen_defend : public AuraScript
2950 {
2951  PrepareAuraScript(spell_gen_defend);
2952 
2953  bool Validate(SpellInfo const* /*spellInfo*/) override
2954  {
2955  return ValidateSpellInfo(
2956  {
2957  SPELL_VISUAL_SHIELD_1,
2958  SPELL_VISUAL_SHIELD_2,
2959  SPELL_VISUAL_SHIELD_3
2960  });
2961  }
2962 
2963  void RefreshVisualShields(AuraEffect const* aurEff, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
2964  {
2965  if (GetCaster())
2966  {
2967  Unit* target = GetTarget();
2968 
2969  for (uint8 i = 0; i < GetSpellInfo()->StackAmount; ++i)
2970  target->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(SPELL_VISUAL_SHIELD_1 + i);
2971 
2972  target->CastSpell(target, SPELL_VISUAL_SHIELD_1 + GetAura()->GetStackAmount() - 1, true, nullptr, aurEff);
2973  }
2974  else
2975  GetTarget()->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(GetId());
2976  }
2977 
2978  void RemoveVisualShields(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
2979  {
2980  for (uint8 i = 0; i < GetSpellInfo()->StackAmount; ++i)
2981  GetTarget()->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(SPELL_VISUAL_SHIELD_1 + i);
2982  }
2983 
2984  void RemoveDummyFromDriver(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
2985  {
2986  if (Unit* caster = GetCaster())
2987  if (TempSummon* vehicle = caster->ToTempSummon())
2988  if (Unit* rider = vehicle->GetSummonerUnit())
2989  rider->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(GetId());
2990  }
2991 
2992  void Register() override
2993  {
2994  SpellInfo const* spell = sSpellMgr->AssertSpellInfo(m_scriptSpellId);
2995 
2996  // Defend spells cast by NPCs (add visuals)
2997  if (spell->Effects[EFFECT_0].ApplyAuraName == SPELL_AURA_MOD_DAMAGE_PERCENT_TAKEN)
2998  {
2999  AfterEffectApply += AuraEffectApplyFn(spell_gen_defend::RefreshVisualShields, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_MOD_DAMAGE_PERCENT_TAKEN, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL_OR_REAPPLY_MASK);
3000  OnEffectRemove += AuraEffectRemoveFn(spell_gen_defend::RemoveVisualShields, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_MOD_DAMAGE_PERCENT_TAKEN, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK);
3001  }
3002 
3003  // Remove Defend spell from player when he dismounts
3004  if (spell->Effects[EFFECT_2].ApplyAuraName == SPELL_AURA_MOD_DAMAGE_PERCENT_TAKEN)
3005  OnEffectRemove += AuraEffectRemoveFn(spell_gen_defend::RemoveDummyFromDriver, EFFECT_2, SPELL_AURA_MOD_DAMAGE_PERCENT_TAKEN, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL);
3006 
3007  // Defend spells cast by players (add/remove visuals)
3008  if (spell->Effects[EFFECT_1].ApplyAuraName == SPELL_AURA_DUMMY)
3009  {
3010  AfterEffectApply += AuraEffectApplyFn(spell_gen_defend::RefreshVisualShields, EFFECT_1, SPELL_AURA_DUMMY, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL_OR_REAPPLY_MASK);
3011  OnEffectRemove += AuraEffectRemoveFn(spell_gen_defend::RemoveVisualShields, EFFECT_1, SPELL_AURA_DUMMY, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK);
3012  }
3013  }
3014 };

3780  75614 - Celestial Steed (spell_celestial_steed)
3781  75973 - X-53 Touring Rocket (spell_x53_touring_rocket) */
3782 class spell_gen_mount : public SpellScript
3783 {
3784  PrepareSpellScript(spell_gen_mount);
3785 
3786 public:
3787  spell_gen_mount(uint32 mount0, uint32 mount60, uint32 mount100, uint32 mount150, uint32 mount280, uint32 mount310) : SpellScript(),
3788  _mount0(mount0), _mount60(mount60), _mount100(mount100), _mount150(mount150), _mount280(mount280), _mount310(mount310) { }
3789 
3790  bool Validate(SpellInfo const* /*spellInfo*/) override
3791  {
3792  if (_mount0 && !sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(_mount0))
3793  return false;
3794  if (_mount60 && !sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(_mount60))
3795  return false;
3796  if (_mount100 && !sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(_mount100))
3797  return false;
3798  if (_mount150 && !sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(_mount150))
3799  return false;
3800  if (_mount280 && !sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(_mount280))
3801  return false;
3802  if (_mount310 && !sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(_mount310))
3803  return false;
3804  return true;
3805  }
3806 
3807  void HandleMount(SpellEffIndex effIndex)
3808  {
3809  PreventHitDefaultEffect(effIndex);
3810 
3811  if (Player* target = GetHitPlayer())
3812  {
3813  uint32 petNumber = target->GetTemporaryUnsummonedPetNumber();
3814  target->SetTemporaryUnsummonedPetNumber(0);
3815 
3816  // Prevent stacking of mounts and client crashes upon dismounting
3817  target->RemoveAurasByType(SPELL_AURA_MOUNTED, ObjectGuid::Empty, GetHitAura());
3818 
3819  // Triggered spell id dependent on riding skill and zone
3820  bool canFly = false;
3821  uint32 map = GetVirtualMapForMapAndZone(target->GetMapId(), target->GetZoneId());
3822  if (map == 530 || (map == 571 && target->HasSpell(SPELL_COLD_WEATHER_FLYING)))
3823  canFly = true;
3824 
3825  AreaTableEntry const* area = sAreaTableStore.LookupEntry(target->GetAreaId());
3826  // Xinef: add battlefield check
3827  Battlefield* Bf = sBattlefieldMgr->GetBattlefieldToZoneId(target->GetZoneId());
3828  if (!area || (canFly && ((area->flags & AREA_FLAG_NO_FLY_ZONE) || (Bf && !Bf->CanFlyIn()))))
3829  canFly = false;
3830 
3831  uint32 mount = 0;
3832  switch (target->GetBaseSkillValue(SKILL_RIDING))
3833  {
3834  case 0:
3835  mount = _mount0;
3836  break;
3837  case 75:
3838  mount = _mount60;
3839  break;
3840  case 150:
3841  mount = _mount100;
3842  break;
3843  case 225:
3844  if (canFly)
3845  mount = _mount150;
3846  else
3847  mount = _mount100;
3848  break;
3849  case 300:
3850  if (canFly)
3851  {
3852  if (_mount310 && target->Has310Flyer(false))
3853  mount = _mount310;
3854  else
3855  mount = _mount280;
3856  }
3857  else
3858  mount = _mount100;
3859  break;
3860  default:
3861  break;
3862  }
3863 
3864  if (mount)
3865  {
3866  PreventHitAura();
3867  target->CastSpell(target, mount, true);
3868  }
3869 
3870  if (petNumber)
3871  target->SetTemporaryUnsummonedPetNumber(petNumber);
3872  }
3873  }
3874 
3875  void Register() override
3876  {
3877  OnEffectHitTarget += SpellEffectFn(spell_gen_mount::HandleMount, EFFECT_2, SPELL_EFFECT_SCRIPT_EFFECT);
3878  }
3879 
3880 private:
3881  uint32 _mount0;
3882  uint32 _mount60;
3883  uint32 _mount100;
3884  uint32 _mount150;
3885  uint32 _mount280;
3886  uint32 _mount310;
3887 };

3966 // 28880, 59542, 59543, 59544, 59545, 59547, 59548 - Gift of the Naaru
3967 class spell_gen_gift_of_naaru : public AuraScript
3968 {
3969  PrepareAuraScript(spell_gen_gift_of_naaru);
3970 
3971  void CalculateAmount(AuraEffect const* aurEff, int32& amount, bool& /*canBeRecalculated*/)
3972  {
3973  if (!GetCaster())
3974  return;
3975 
3976  float heal = 0.0f;
3977  switch (GetSpellInfo()->SpellFamilyName)
3978  {
3979  case SPELLFAMILY_MAGE:
3980  case SPELLFAMILY_WARLOCK:
3981  case SPELLFAMILY_PRIEST:
3982  heal = 1.885f * float(GetCaster()->SpellBaseDamageBonusDone(GetSpellInfo()->GetSchoolMask()));
3983  break;
3984  case SPELLFAMILY_PALADIN:
3985  case SPELLFAMILY_SHAMAN:
3986  heal = std::max(1.885f * float(GetCaster()->SpellBaseDamageBonusDone(GetSpellInfo()->GetSchoolMask())), 1.1f * float(GetCaster()->GetTotalAttackPowerValue(BASE_ATTACK)));
3987  break;
3988  case SPELLFAMILY_WARRIOR:
3989  case SPELLFAMILY_HUNTER:
3990  case SPELLFAMILY_DEATHKNIGHT:
3991  heal = 1.1f * float(std::max(GetCaster()->GetTotalAttackPowerValue(BASE_ATTACK), GetCaster()->GetTotalAttackPowerValue(RANGED_ATTACK)));
3992  break;
3993  case SPELLFAMILY_GENERIC:
3994  default:
3995  break;
3996  }
3997 
3998  int32 healTick = floor(heal / aurEff->GetTotalTicks());
3999  amount += int32(std::max(healTick, 0));
4000  }
4001 
4002  void Register() override
4003  {
4004  DoEffectCalcAmount += AuraEffectCalcAmountFn(spell_gen_gift_of_naaru::CalculateAmount, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_PERIODIC_HEAL);
4005  }
4006 };

4013 
4014 /* 57669 - Replenishment
4015  61782 - Infinite Replenishment + Wisdom */
4016 class spell_gen_replenishment : public SpellScript
4017 {
4018  PrepareSpellScript(spell_gen_replenishment);
4019 
4020  void RemoveInvalidTargets(std::list<WorldObject*>& targets)
4021  {
4022  // In arenas Replenishment may only affect the caster
4023  if (Player* caster = GetCaster()->ToPlayer())
4024  {
4025  if (caster->InArena())
4026  {
4027  targets.clear();
4028  targets.push_back(caster);
4029  return;
4030  }
4031  }
4032 
4033  targets.remove_if(Acore::PowerCheck(POWER_MANA, false));
4034 
4035  uint8 const maxTargets = 10;
4036 
4037  if (targets.size() > maxTargets)
4038  {
4039  targets.sort(Acore::PowerPctOrderPred(POWER_MANA));
4040  targets.resize(maxTargets);
4041  }
4042  }
4043 
4044  void Register() override
4045  {
4046  OnObjectAreaTargetSelect += SpellObjectAreaTargetSelectFn(spell_gen_replenishment::RemoveInvalidTargets, EFFECT_ALL, TARGET_UNIT_CASTER_AREA_RAID);
4047  }
4048 };

4070  break;
4071  }
4072  }
